skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: body spelling bee
des: This quiz style skill lets you choose a category of organ system and gives you a word to spell. You will see if you spelled the word correctly or not and also how to spell it right. You can play as many rounds in all categories as you want.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
